    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Process of separating grain from straw, chaff, weeds and other debris by flailing, or beating it, by treading, or walking animals over the mowed grain, or later by feeding the stalks of grain through machines.</Note_Text>
